{"tid":687323,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"內會否決馬逢國髮Gel風波辯論","createTime":"2018-06-02T07:04:23.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-02T08:22:53.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"597cb7e9edd544b6856dd202f772bda6af76778e","tid":687323,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T07:04:23.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180602/20408928\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180602%2F20408928&d=erNGLdZGAKQJnf37bPnvCKWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=3600fa9c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180602%2F20408928&h=e6c6baed\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180602/20408928</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年06月02日 <br />\n<br />\n內會否決馬逢國髮Gel風波辯論<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180602/large/a0804a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180602%2Flarge%2Fa0804a.gif&h=f734c659&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■范國威昨在立會諷刺馬逢國帶Gel上機無視法紀。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】建制派議員馬逢國涉「撻朵」攜帶髮膠登機，公民黨議員譚文豪要求就事件在大會上提出休會辯論，議案在內會最終在建制派反對下被否決。譚文豪發言時直問，「究竟係法治重要定係髮Gel重要？」他呼籲議員同事勿濫用權力，否則香港只會越來越禮崩樂壞。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「咁嘅髮量仲帶Gel」<br />\n<br />\n馬逢國的髮Gel事件在內會引起一陣爭論，民主黨林卓廷指，「法治、髮線、髮型、髮膠都要捍衞，但最重要都係法治」，他批評馬逢國為了捍衞髮膠無視制度，馬亦在事件中提到議員身份和機場管理層名字，質疑「呢個唔係特殊對待係咩呢？」<br />\n<br />\n建制派議員則繼續為馬逢國護航，民建聯蔣麗芸指，作為立法會議員應守法，但休會辯論是將「正（經）事放埋一邊」，如果每個議員都濫用休會辯論，「正（經）事就會唔使做、會就唔使開」。工聯會黃國健批評提出休會辯論是「抽水動作」，又指馬逢國最大錯處是「你頭髮咁嘅量仲堅持帶髮Gel」，沒有其他不妥的地方。部份建制派議員發言時，內會主席李慧琼都未能忍笑。<br />\n<br />\n至於馬逢國，於會上再次就事件公眾及涉事人員致歉，直言事件是因為誤解，強調自己未有要求對方予特殊對待，已經去信要求機管局不要懲處有關人員。他並去信保安事務委員會解釋事發經過，並再次道歉。<br />\n<br />\n■記者陳嘉裕  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n街工5執委退黨　梁耀忠：尊重決定<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n不滿欽點李卓人　民協要求初選"},{"pid":"4ba46c22dfda38bcac6fc86f0790f3980c3b2a80","tid":687323,"uid":13718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T07:49:54.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">「法治、髮線、髮型、髮膠都要捍衞，但最重要都係法治」</span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2bb1ba6a93e490b7051c429985a3d30c55b49327","tid":687323,"uid":104793,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T08:11:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><br />\n<br />\n至於馬逢國，於會上再次就事件公眾及涉事人員致歉，直言事件是因為誤解，強調自己未有要求對方予特殊對待，<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">已經去信要求機管局不要懲處有關人員</span></span>。他並去信保安事務委員會解釋事發經過，並再次道歉。<br />\n<br />\n</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n又躂朵, 以為自己邊個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n而家條友違反國際民航組織指引同航空公司規例放生咗你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唔罰佢罰邊個<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22f8be8fe154e7f0849361f23fe8df22308406ea","tid":687323,"uid":76063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T08:13:23.000Z","msg":"this is hong kong"},{"pid":"3e3aa121a13b045142d7d297149a88e03cdeb37f","tid":687323,"uid":182475,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T08:15:09.000Z","msg":"我比較想知佢點解會覺得自己要帶200ml gel 先夠用。佢係咪唔止用來 gel 頭頂? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab06df35308640a0b15299d493c1ce9425d6fef8","tid":687323,"uid":126044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4ba46c22dfda38bcac6fc86f0790f3980c3b2a80","tid":687323,"uid":13718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T07:49:54.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">「法治、髮線、髮型、髮膠都要捍衞，但最重要都係法治」</span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T08:18:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 俾人抽爆<br />\n<br />\n呢條友真係無髮無天，人地唔俾佢帶gel佢就髮脾氣，髮神經！"},{"pid":"dbba7067735b2bd5e844a639cdb5293eafef97fa","tid":687323,"uid":174013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3e3aa121a13b045142d7d297149a88e03cdeb37f","tid":687323,"uid":182475,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T08:15:09.000Z","msg":"我比較想知佢點解會覺得自己要帶200ml gel 先夠用。佢係咪唔止用來 gel 頭頂? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T08:19:03.000Z","msg":"果隻GASTBY我用過<br />\n根本無乜HOLD力<br />\n除非用好多"},{"pid":"d653ba5d91118723e00770024f15f17031c0b674","tid":687323,"uid":123264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T08:19:57.000Z","msg":"「究竟係法治重要定係髮Gel重要？」<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac0e3cdb3ba0dce5c936edd2949bf5f259904cee","tid":687323,"uid":69098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T08:22:53.000Z","msg":"卡片蘇：屌你老母！！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}